Providence will be featured in the upcoming @frontlinepbs #Coronavirus #pandemic special report on Tuesday, April 21 at 6 pm PDT. Set your DVR and get an inside look at how we were the first health system in the nation to handle the COVID-19 pandemic.

Like all healthcare institutions coping with the national PPE shortage, we have followed CDC and other expert guidelines throughout the crisis to ensure every caregiver receives one N95 mask at the beginning of each shift to care for COVID-19 patients persons under investigation.
